  ANIMALS OF THE WORLD
============================================================

Name:         Monarch Butterfly
Scientific:   Danaus plexippus
Class:        Insecta
Habitat:      Meadows
Diet:         Herbivore
Lifespan:     0.25 years
Weight:       0.0005 kg
Status:       Endangered
Fact:         Migrates 4,800 km; uses Earth's magnetic field for navigation

Name:         Blue Whale
Scientific:   Balaenoptera musculus
Class:        Mammalia
Habitat:      Ocean
Diet:         Carnivore (krill)
Lifespan:     80 years
Weight:       150000 kg
Status:       Endangered
Fact:         Largest animal ever known; heart is size of a small car

Name:         Hummingbird
Scientific:   Trochilidae
Class:        Aves
Habitat:      Forest
Diet:         Omnivore
Lifespan:     5 years
Weight:       0.003 kg
Status:       Varies
Fact:         Only bird that can fly backwards; heart beats 1,260 times per minute

